## üèõÔ∏è ARTICLE VII: THE TAXONOMY OF ECONOMIC FACTORS
The framework shall expand to address the following primary questions in order of priority. Each factor must be developed as a standalone module within the /scripts directory to ensure modularity and prevent system sprawl1111.
Priority	Economic Question	Primary Signals (Tier 1 & 2)
01	Household Stress	Rent-to-income, credit card balances, delinquencies, and inflation-adjusted wages2222.
02	Housing Health	Price-to-wage growth, mortgage rates, inventory levels, and days on market3.
