## üõ°Ô∏è ARTICLE X: QUALITY ASSURANCE & AUDIT
‚Ä¢	Section 10.01: Regression Testing: The integration of a new factor (e.g., Factor 02) shall not break the automation, SQL integrity, or agent logic of existing factors (e.g., Factor 01)13.
‚Ä¢	Section 10.02: Memory Continuity: All agents must write their narratives and findings to a central agent_memory table in PostgreSQL14. This ensures the AI maintains historical context and "remembers" trends across all subjects over time15151515.
